data.description: Jubilee a 55 & Older Community...Open & airy Southpoint floor plan features beautiful hardwood fls throughout the dining, hall & kitchen areas, great room w/newer carpets & slider to private covered patio & fenced rear yard. Kitchen w/quartz counters, center eating island w/custom pendent lights, full height tile back-splash & stainless appliances. Primary bdrm w/ample space for a king size bdrm, walk-in closet & private bath w/quartz counter top w/tile accent, lg shower & separate commode. 2nd bdrm w/easy access to full bath making it perfect for guests. The rear yard offers privacy & low maintenance landscaping w/over size patio. Laundry rm w/custom storage cabinet & W/D, 2 car garage w/elec opener. Energy Efficient w/gas furnace w/AC
